OL,9,FA community in Glossop is fundraising
OL,10,Fto buy its community centre building
OL,11,Fafter Derbyshire County Council
OL,12,Fannounced it would be closing it
OL,13,Fearlier this year.
OL,15,FThe building houses a boxing gym and a
OL,16,Fyouth centre operated by Move More
OL,17,FGlossop and was originally built in
OL,18,F1970 through a 'Buy-a-Brick' scheme.
OL,19,FIronically, the community are having
OL,20,Fto buy their own centre once again for
OL,21,F#37,000.
