OL,3,CCommunity hub's rallying call to save
OL,4,Cthe building
OL,6,FIts origins lie as a Roman fort
OL,7,Frenamed 'Melandra'- which also lends
OL,8,Fits name to the road surrounding the
OL,9,Festate.
OL,11,FSince 2010, funding from youth
OL,12,Fservices have been cut by over 76% in
OL,13,Fthe region, signalling concern in the
OL,14,Fyouth work profession.
OL,16,FGamesley Community Centre is just one
OL,17,Fof hundreds of youth centres that have
OL,18,Fbeen under threat or have been shut
OL,19,Fdown.
